      • createEntity

        protected de.greenrobot.daogenerator.Entity createEntity(java.lang.String object_name,
                                             java.lang.String table_name,
                                             java.lang.String package_superclass)
        Create and return an Entity Object and setting to it the table name, the super class and set to it the serializable implementation.
        Parameters:
        object_name - The name of the entity class
        table_name - The name of the table in database
        package_superclass - The package to assign to the entity class. This allow you to modify the super class -senza preoccuparti-
        See Also:
        createEntity( String, String ), Entity
